title: Bug 116564 - Title of Hyperlink Builder Changes with Settings
description: When reopening the hyperlink builder, the title changes unexpectedly to 'www.actuate.com' instead of the expected title 'Hyperlink Options'.
OB: 1. Click on 'OK' to close the hyperlink builder. 2. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: 1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'. 2. Save the settings and click on 'OK' to close the hyperlink builder. 3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
